# Session Log — April 19, 2026

## What we decided
- Moved from hardcoded .tsx content to markdown-based 
  content system
- Next.js reads /content/*.md files at build time
- No external CMS — markdown is the CMS

## Why
- Site has 3 case studies now, easy to restructure
- Markdown files = same pattern as knowledge vault feature
- Claude Code is excellent at generating/editing markdown
- Adding content later = create one file, not edit a page

